item.title: SPRING GARDEN ON FYAH!
item.description: The Question Barbados is hot. It was always hot, its a tropical paradise in the Caribbean its supposed to be hot but for Bajans, in recent times it feels hotter than ever before. The heat is oppressive , making a five minute walk at midday seem like a journey through hell and forget about driving with your window down to enjoy the breeze. This is no surprise, everyone knows the earth is getting warmer.

item.title: About Me
item.description: Hi I’m Jamaal Roach and welcome to my blog. This tiny corner of the internet is a space for my fidling around with the statistical R to analyse and visualise data. The posts will mostly be driven by curiosity where a random thought sends me on a quest to find an answer from the available information. I intend to cover a wide range but don’t be too alarmed if there are more than a few posts about football #FC Barcelona.
